videos.description: Ray Spalding gets his defender to bite on a pump fake and drops in a one-handed shot despite the foul for the Cardinals.
videos.headline: Miami's Spalding does work in the paint

videos.description: Lonnie Walker IV attacks the rim and finishes with a beautiful left-handed layup for the Canes.
videos.headline: Miami's Walker hits pretty lefty layup

videos.description: Quentin Snider gets the dish and splashes home a  3-pointer for the Cardinals in the second half.
videos.headline: Louisville's Snider on target from deep

videos.description: Sam Waardenburg trails the play after a bad turnover and comes up with a huge hustle block for the Hurricanes.
videos.headline: Miami's Waardenburg comes out of nowhere for block

videos.description: Anas Mahmoud gets a dish from Quentin Snider and slams home the two-handed jam for the Cardinals.
videos.headline: Louisville's Mahmoud throws down alley-oop

videos.description: Dewan Huell gets a perfect bounce pass from Lonnie Walker IV and finishes with the flush in OT.
videos.headline: Miami's Huell slams home transition dunk
